prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: AI Apps in Plain Language
prompt.content: Promptbook is an ecosystem of projects and tools for writing AI applications in plain human language. It includes a markup language called Book, an engine to run Book applications, and a web-based editor called Promptbook Studio.
